list.title: What is TikTok slang?
list.description: If you’re familiar with the language of online video, you’ll recognize a number of TikTok slang terms. Most people use the term “pov,” which stands for point of view. Using this term to describe your video will make your viewers feel more connected with you. Unlike in real life, pov can be used with any video type.
